king part-time at a rental-studio space.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"So I came to check out CiRCLE to see what's going on with the competition.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"Just joking. I had nothing to do, so I came by to hang out for a bit.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"Not to be nosy or anything, but it seems like CiRCLE is seeing way more business than before.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"When I was walking here, I saw a lot of people carrying instruments. I think that's great.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf_left01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"By the way, the other day, Poppin'Party celebrated its first anniversary of passing the audition at SPACE.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"Arisa and I planned a surprise for the others. We showed them a video of us playing the last show at the venue.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"It was! We had so much fun watching it! We all started remembering things from that day.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"And it made me think.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"SPACE might be gone, but the heart and soul of that place are still around.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"Like it's inside of all of us.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"... Huh? What am I talking about?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev83-me2-014","volume":1}],"speed":